titleStmt.title: A declaration and protestation of VVill: Prynne and Cle: VValker, Esquires, Members of the House of Commons against the present actings and proceedings of the Generall, and Generall Councell of the army, and their faction now remaining and sitting in the said House.
titleStmt.author: Prynne, William, 1600-1669.
Walker, Clement, 1595-1651.

notesStmt.note: Dated and signed at end: 19 Janu. 1648. Will: Prynne, Cle: Walker.
